171 A.3d 1259 SHAKEEM MALIK HOLMES, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. JERSEY CITY POLICE DEPARTMENT, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-73 Sept. Tern 2017

079457 October 20, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001634-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
